{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-149","title":"生气发怒","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":752,"pageEnd":756,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":22,"duplicateEntryCount":21,"pages":[{"number":752,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"149 生气发怒"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"anger [ˈæŋɡə(r)]","headword":"anger"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.愤怒，生气"},{"type":"note","text":"◎anger at因…而引发的怒火/in anger生气地，愤怒地"},{"type":"entry","text":"annoyance [əˈnɔɪəns]","headword":"annoyance"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.恼怒"},{"type":"entry","text":"irritation [ˌɪrɪˈteɪʃn]","headword":"irritation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.愤怒；激怒"}]},{"number":753,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"angry [ˈæŋɡri]","headword":"angry"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.生气的，愤怒的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be angry with sb.生某人的气/get angry生气"},{"type":"entry","text":"be angry at对…生气","headword":"be angry at"},{"type":"entry","text":"annoying [əˈnɔɪɪŋ]","headword":"annoying"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.使人颇为生气的；恼人的"},{"type":"entry","text":"mad [mæd]","headword":"mad"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.狂怒的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be mad at对…非常愤怒"}]},{"number":754,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"infuriating [ɪnˈfjʊərieɪtɪŋ]","headword":"infuriating"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.令人大怒的"},{"type":"entry","text":"aggravating [ˈæɡrəveɪtɪŋ]","headword":"aggravating"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.激怒的，惹恼的"},{"type":"entry","text":"cross [krɒs]","headword":"cross"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.乖戾的；生气的"}]},{"number":755,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"angrily [ˈæŋɡrəli]","headword":"angrily"},{"type":"definition","text":"ad. 愤怒地，生气地"},{"type":"entry","text":"to rouse one's anger 把某人惹火","headword":"to rouse one's anger"},{"type":"entry","text":"out of control 失去控制","headword":"out of control"},{"type":"entry","text":"take offence 生气","headword":"take offence"},{"type":"entry","text":"burn up 生气，恼火","headword":"burn up"},{"type":"entry","text":"have a fit 大发雷霆","headword":"have a fit"},{"type":"entry","text":"tick off 惹某人生气","headword":"tick off"},{"type":"entry","text":"throw a fit 大发脾气","headword":"throw a fit"},{"type":"entry","text":"drive crazy 将…逼得发疯","headword":"drive crazy"},{"type":"entry","text":"furious with anger 狂怒","headword":"furious with anger"},{"type":"entry","text":"get out 出去，离开","headword":"get out"},{"type":"entry","text":"piss off 立即走开","headword":"piss off"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"}]},{"number":756,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：What happened in there?（那边出什么事儿了？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：He lost his temper.（他发脾气呢。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：So why won't his wife speak to him?（他老婆为什么不跟他说"},{"type":"text","text":"话？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Because he got fired from his job and then he took his anger out"},{"type":"text","text":"on his child. （因为他被炒了鱿鱼，然后把气撒在孩子身上。）"}]}]}